title: Import of creamery butter in Canada 2021
summary: The graph shows the Import of creamery butter ( in Tonnes ) in Canada the year 2021 .
Import is very different over the year .
While a significant decrease in Import can be observed from January to February , Import continues to rise until April , reaching its annual maximum of more than 42000 Tonnes .
gold: The chart is showing the amount of import of creamery butter in tonnes in Canada over the course of 12 consecutive months of the year 2021 . Multiple peaks are visible , with two priminant ones in May and October . Most prominent dip occurs in February .
